gurmukhi: ਅਛੇਦ ਛੇਦ ਹੈ ਸਦਾ ਅਗੰਜ ਗੰਜ ਗੰਜ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Achhed Chhed Hai Sadaa Agadg Gadj Gadj Hai||
translation: He always assails the unassailable, He is the Destroyer of the Indestructible.

gurmukhi: ਅਭੂਤ ਅਭੇਖ ਹੈ ਬਲੀ ਅਰੂਪ ਰਾਗ ਰੰਗ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Abhoot Abhekh Hai Balee Aroop Raag Ran Hai||
translation: His Elementless Garb is Powerful, He is the Original Form of Sound and Colour.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਦ੍ਵੈਖ ਹੈ ਨ ਭੇਖ ਹੈ ਨ ਕਾਮ ਕ੍ਰੋਧ ਕਰਮ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Dvaikh Hai Na Bhekh Hai Na Kaam Krodh Karam Hai||
translation: He is without malice, garb, lust anger and action.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਜਾਤ ਹੈ ਨ ਪਾਤ ਹੈ ਨ ਚਿੱਤ੍ਰ ਚਿਹਨ ਬਰਨ ਹੈ ॥੧੫॥੧੭੫॥
transliteration: Na Jaat Hai Na Paat Hai Na Chittra Chihan Baran Hai||15||175||
translation: He is without caste, lineage, picture, mark and colour.15.175.

gurmukhi: ਬਿਅੰਤ ਹੈ ਅਨੰਤ ਹੈ ਅਨੰਤ ਤੇਜ ਜਾਨੀਅੈ ॥
transliteration: Biant Hai Anant Hai Anant Tej Jaanooai||
translation: He is Limitless, endless and be comprehended as consisting of endless Glory.

gurmukhi: ਅਭੂਮ ਅਭਿੱਜ ਹੈ ਸਦਾ ਅਛਿੱਜ ਤੇਜ ਮਾਨੀਅੈ ॥
transliteration: Abhoom Abhijj Hai Sadaa Achhijj Tej Maanooai||
translation: He is unearthly and unappeasable and be considered as consisting of unassailable Glory.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਅਾਧ ਹੈ ਨ ਬਿਅਾਧ ਹੈ ਅਗਾਧ ਰੈਪ ਲੇਖੀਅੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Aadh Hai Na Biaadh Hai Agaddh Roop Lekhooai||
translation: He is without the ailments of body and mind and be Known as the lord of Unfathomable form.

gurmukhi: ਅਦੋਖ ਹੈ ਅਦਾਗ ਹੈ ਅਛੈ ਪ੍ਰਤਾਪ ਪੇਖੀਅੈ ॥੧੬॥੧੭੬॥
transliteration: Adokh Hai Adaag Hai Achhai Prataap Pekhooai||16||176||
translation: He is Without blemish and stain and be visualised as consisting of Indestructible Glory .16.176

gurmukhi: ਨ ਕਰਮ ਹੈ ਨ ਭਰਮ ਹੈ ਨ ਧਰਮ ਕੋ ਪ੍ਰਭਾੳੁ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Karam Hai Na Bharam Hai Na Dharam Ko Prabhaao Hai||
translation: He is beyond the impact of action, illusion and religion.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਜੰਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਤੰਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਮੰਤ੍ਰ ਕੋ ਰਲਾੳੁ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Jantra Hai Na Tantra Hai Na Mantra Ko Ralaao Hai||
translation: He is neither Yantra, nor Tantra nor a blend of slander.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਛਲ ਹੈ ਨ ਛਿਦ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਛਿਦ੍ਰ ਕੋ ਸਰੂਪ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Chhal Hai Na Chhidra Hai Na Chhidra Ko Saroophai||
translation: He is neither deceit, nor malice nor a form of slander.

gurmukhi: ਅਭੰਗ ਹੈ ਅਨੰਗ ਹੈ ਅਗੰਜ ਸੀ ਬਿਭੂਤ ਹੈ ॥੧੭॥੧੭੭॥
transliteration: Abhan Hai Anan Hai Agadj Soo Bibhoot Hai||17||177||
translation: He is Indivisible, limbless and treasure of unending equipment.17.177.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਕਾਮ ਹੈ ਨ ਗਾਧ ਹੈ ਨ ਬਿਅਾਧ ਕੋ ਬਿਚਾਰ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Kaam Hai Na Krodh Hai Na Lobh Moh Kaar Hai||
translation: He is without the activity of lust, anger, greed and attachment.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਅਾਧ ਹੈ ਨ ਕ੍ਰੋਧ ਹੈ ਨ ਲੋਭ ਮੋਹ ਕਾਰ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Na Aadh Hai Na Gaddh Hai Na Roop Rekh Raar Hai||
translation: He, the Unfathomable Lord, is without the concepts of the ailments of the body and mind.
